Thank you for bringing to our attention the issues encountered following the monthly auto patching activity on one of our Zabbix proxy servers.

We sincerely apologize for any inconvenience caused by the server not booting up for a few hours post-maintenance. We understand that this disruption has resulted in gaps in the graphs, and we recognize the importance of maintaining continuity in monitoring systems.

Rest assured, our team is actively working to address this issue and ensure that such disruptions are minimized in the future. Additionally, we will ensure to provide advance notification of any planned maintenance activities to mitigate any potential impact on operations.

Please feel free to reach out if you have any further concerns or questions regarding this matter. We appreciate your understanding and patience as we work towards resolving this issue.
